ProductUrlStructureTypes.Name: ProductSeo
ProductUrlStructureTypes.Description: Represents the URL structure for product only (e.g. '/product-seo-name')

ProductUrlStructureTypes.Name: CategoryProduct
ProductUrlStructureTypes.Description: Represents the URL structure for category (the most nested), then product (e.g. '/category-seo-name/product-seo-name')

ProductUrlStructureTypes.Name: ManufacturerProduct
ProductUrlStructureTypes.Description: Represents the URL structure for manufacturer, then product (e.g. '/manufacturer-seo-name/product-seo-name')
